   ``It happened very, very suddenly,'' Cuomo said after
Wednesday's excitement. ``We joined the chase.''
   Cuomo was in Harlem on his way to a school to promote school
construction legislation when he and two state troopers in his car
spotted police officers chasing a man with a bag of tokens around
his neck.
   Cuomo said his driver, Trooper Mary Ellen Fitzpatrick, tried to
