her nose to correct a deviated septum. Miss Idaho Susan Kae Hart _
the only one to confess to speeding tickets _ said she had plastic
surgery on her earlobes to correct a blockage problem.
   The televised finale of the 62nd Miss America pageant will take
place Saturday.
